org.openimaj.image.objectdetection.filtering

Class OpenCVGrouping

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.image.objectdetection.filtering.OpenCVGrouping
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DetectionFilter<Rectangle,ObjectIntPair<Rectangle>>

    public final class OpenCVGrouping
extends Object
implements DetectionFilter<Rectangle,ObjectIntPair<Rectangle>>
    Filter to perform the grouping of detection rectangles in the way OpenCV does. Basically the groups are formed by grouping together all the rectangles that overlap by a certain amount. For each group, the mean rectangle is calculated. Groups that have too little support are removed, as are groups that are enclosed by other groups.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
